public abstract class ModelElementImpl extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container implements ModelElement
An implementation of the model object 'Model Element'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Markers
  • Uris
  • Description
  • Uuid
  • Action Prototype
  • Representations
  • Annotations

    • resolveProxy

      protected <E extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> E resolveProxy(E eObject)
      If argument is a proxy - resolves it. If it is not resolved throws ConfigurationException with a org.nasdanika.common.persistence.Marker from the proxy if it is org.nasdanika.common.persistence.Marked and has a marker or from this object.
